    'tag%3Agoogle.com%2C2005%3Areader/item/afc790c9afda3803.html':'<p>I decided it would be fun to do something different this week and choose prints for <a href="http://www.society6.com/prints/design-milk?curator=designmilk">The Design Milk Dairy</a> art collection based on how they would look best as iPhone cases or skins. I found a few new patterned ones that I thought would be great for those of you considering getting an iPhone 4 now that the iPhone 4S is arriving on the scene.</p><p><img title="Fresh From The Dairy: Patterned iPhone Cases" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/arnsdorfss11.jpg" alt="Fresh From The Dairy: Patterned iPhone Cases" width="500" height="500"></p><p><a href="http://society6.com/product/Arnsdorf-SS11-Crystal-Pattern_iPhone-Case?tag=design-milk&amp;curator=designmilk">Arnsdorf SS11 Crystal Pattern by RoAndCo </a></p><p><img title="Fresh From The Dairy: Patterned iPhone Cases" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/bizzybizzy-kosek.jpg" alt="Fresh From The Dairy: Patterned iPhone Cases" width="500" height="500"></p><p><a href="http://society6.com/product/BizzyBizzy_iPhone-Case?tag=design-milk&amp;curator=designmilk">BizzyBizzy by Kate Kosek</a></p><p><img title="Fresh From The Dairy: Patterned iPhone Cases" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/bw2-katherine-farah.jpg" alt="Fresh From The Dairy: Patterned iPhone Cases" width="500" height="500"></p><p><a href="http://society6.com/product/Black-and-White-2-jNQ_iPhone-Case?tag=design-milk&amp;curator=designmilk">Black and White 2 by Katherine Farah</a></p><p>Here are a few of the prints previously added to <a href="http://www.society6.com/prints/design-milk?curator=designmilk">The Design Milk Dairy</a> that also work really well as iPhone cases:</p><p><img title="Fresh From The Dairy: Patterned iPhone Cases" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/iphone-cases-patterns.jpg" alt="Fresh From The Dairy: Patterned iPhone Cases" width="500" height="500"></p><p><em>From top left