    'tag%3Agoogle.com%2C2005%3Areader/item/837d65b932590e68.html':'<p><img title="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/09/shadow-construction.jpg" alt="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" width="500" height="375"></p><p><a href="http://www.studiomarte.nl">Marte Haverkamp</a> graduated last year from School of the Arts Utrecht, Netherlands and her graduation project, Shadow Construction.</p><p><span></span>She explains, \u201cI have been fascinated by shadows for a long time and I wanted to do something with that. By capturing shadows of different objects and then materializing them, I came onto new objects. Objects with a high level of recognition that make you look twice.\u201d</p><p><img title="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/09/shadow-construction-chair-1.jpg" alt="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" width="500" height="591"></p><p><img title="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/09/shadow-construction-chair-2.jpg" alt="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" width="500" height="588"></p><p><img title="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/09/shadow-construction-crate.jpg" alt="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" width="500" height="375"></p><p><img title="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/09/shadow-construction-ladder.jpg" alt="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" width="500" height="512"></p><p><img title="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/09/shadow-construction-laundry-basket.jpg" alt="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" width="500" height="375"></p><p><img title="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/09/shadow-construction-scissors.jpg" alt="Shadow Construction by Marte Haverkamp" width="500" height="332"></p><p>Now, she\u2019s interested in exploring these conceptual objects further, giving them more practical function. I\u2019m interested to see what she comes up with.</p><hr><b>Share This:</b> <a href="http://twitter.com/home?status=Reading%20Shadow%20Construction%20by%20Marte%20Haverkamp%20on%20@designmilk:%20http://design-milk.com/shadow-construction-by-marte-haverkamp/" title="Tweet This">Twitter</a> | <a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http://design-milk.com/shadow-construction-by-marte-haverkamp/&amp;title=Shadow%20Construction%20by%20Marte%20Haverkamp" title="Share this on Facebook">Facebook</a> | Discover more great design by following Design Milk on <a href="http://twitter.com/designmilk">Twitter</a> and <a href="http://www.facebook.com/designmilk">Facebook</a>.<hr> <small>\xa9 2011 <a href="http://design-milk.com">Design Milk</a> | Posted by Jaime in <a href="http://design-milk.com/category/home-furnishings/" title="View all posts in Home Furnishings" rel="category tag">Home Furnishings</a> | <a href="http://design-milk.com/shadow-construction-by-marte-haverkamp/">Permalink</a> | <a href="http://design-milk.com/shadow-construction-by-marte-haverkamp/#comments">No comments</a></small><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/design-milk/~4/FiyjdSjOQjg" height="1" width="1">', 
    'tag%3Agoogle.com%2C2005%3Areader/item/59ae211d94c4692e.html':'<p><img title="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/fibulae-boffo-3.jpg" alt="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" width="500" height="333"></p><p>Fibulae is an 1800-square-foot pop-up shop/installation by <a href="http://theverymany.com/">Marc Fornes &amp; THEVERYMANY</a> and <a href="http://focuslighting.com/">Focus Lighting Inc.</a> made to display the jewelry of LA-based designer, <a href="http://www.ireneneuwirth.com/">Irene Neuwirth</a>.</p><p><span></span>Kind of part space pod world, part biology lab, the jewelry is displayed in 19 illuminated glowing gold and glass pods, which create an other-worldy landscape. The installation is made from 7,000 brushed aluminum parts that were pre-cut and assembled on-site.</p><p><img title="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/fibulae-boffo-4.jpg" alt="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" width="500" height="375"></p><p><img title="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/fibulae-boffo-1.jpg" alt="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" width="500" height="333"></p><p><img title="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/fibulae-boffo-2.jpg" alt="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" width="500" height="333"></p><p><img title="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/fibulae-boffo-5.jpg" alt="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" width="500" height="333"></p><p><img title="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/fibulae-boffo-6.jpg" alt="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" width="500" height="333"></p><p><img title="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/fibulae-boffo-7.jpg" alt="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" width="500" height="333"></p><p><img title="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/fibulae-boffo-8.jpg" alt="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" width="500" height="333"></p><p><img title="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/fibulae-boffo-9.jpg" alt="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" width="500" height="750"></p><p><img title="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" src="http://design-milk.com/images/2011/10/fibulae-boffo-10.jpg" alt="Fibulae Installation by Marc Fornes and Focus Lighting" width="500" height="750"></p><p>Part of the the <a href="http://www.boffo-ny.org/">Boffo Building Fashion series</a>, the installation will only be open through October 12, 2011, so get over to 57 Walker Street, between Church and Broadway in NYC and check it out before it\u2019s gone.</p><p>Photos by Evan Joseph.</p><hr><b>Share This:</b> <a href="http://twitter.com/home?status=Reading%20Fibulae%20Installation%20by%20Marc%20Fornes%20and%20Focus%20Lighting%20on%20@designmilk:%20http://design-milk.com/fibulae-installation-by-marc-fornes-and-focus-lighting/" title="Tweet This">Twitter</a> | <a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http://design-milk.com/fibulae-installation-by-marc-fornes-and-focus-lighting/&amp;title=Fibulae%20Installation%20by%20Marc%20Fornes%20and%20Focus%20Lighting" title="Share this on Facebook">Facebook</a> | Discover more great design by following Design Milk on <a href="http://twitter.com/designmilk">Twitter</a> and <a href="http://www.facebook.com/designmilk">Facebook</a>.<hr> <small>\xa9 2011 <a href="http://design-milk.com">Design Milk</a> | Posted by Jaime in <a href="http://d