Architects and Engineers:<br>\n<a href="http://www.world-architects.com/en/projects/project-current-review/32179_laird_norton_addition_at_the_winona_county_history_center"><img alt="this week&#39;s Building of the Week" src="http://files3.world-architects.com/projects/32179/images/390:w/winonahistory3.jpg" title="Current Building of the Week on american-architects.com" width="200"></a><br>\n<br>\n<span style="font-weight:bold">Some unrelated links for your enjoyment:</span><br>\n<blockquote>\n<a href="http://artchitectured.blogspot.com/">ArchitectuRed</a><br>\nNewish blog by a NYC-based student. (Added  to sidebar under Blogs \xbb Architecture.)<br>\n<br>\n<a href="http://designblog.rietveldacademie.nl/">Designblog</a><br>\n"An online research project initiated by Henk Groenendijk at the Gerrit Rietveld Academie." (Added  to sidebar under Blogs \xbb Design.)<br>\n<br>\n<a href="http://midcenturymundane.wordpress.com/">Mid-Century Mundane</a><br>\n"The most exciting of mundane mid\u2011century architecture." (Added  to sidebar under Blogs \xbb Architecture.)<br>\n<br>\n<a href="http://softlabnyc.com/news/?p=1541">San Gennaro North Gate</a><br>\nAn installation at Houston and Mulberry Streets greets visitors to the San Gennaro Festival, Sep. 15-25.<br>\n<br>\n<a href="http://myriammahiques.blogspot.com/">Thoughts on Architecture and Urbanism</a><br>\n"These are notes and articles based on Architecture and Urbanism by Myriam Mahiques." (Added to sidebar  under Blogs \xbb Architecture.)</blockquote>\n<div><img width="1" height="1" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/6531343-3297102122786222272?l=archidose.blogspot.com" alt=""></div><p><iframe src="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~ah/f/boc0kauf7mi6m5sj0ch39v158c/300/250?ca=1&amp;fh=280#http%3A%2F%2Farchidose.blogspot.com%2F2011%2F09%2Fmonday-monday_19.html" width="100%" height="280" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0"></iframe></p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/blogspot/eTHYkZ/~4/GXjUkk9v9J4" height="1" width="1">', 
