    'tag%3Agoogle.com%2C2005%3Areader/item/b151cba658f22488.html':'<p></p><p style="text-align:center"><a href="http://leberpr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/123991926CarolynLeber97201142441PM.jpg"><img style="border:1px solid black" title="Betsy Johnson&#39;s Tour de Fashion Bike" src="http://leberpr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/123991926CarolynLeber97201142441PM.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="651"></a></p>\n<p>If you\u2019re in the city for FashionWeek, look for the <a href="http://www.fashioncenter.com/neighborhood/tour-de-fashion">Tour de Fashion bikes</a> that will be rolling around.\xa0 Made available through the Fashion Center, the fleet was purchased from Bowery Lane Bicycles, and have been embellished by some of New York\u2019s top fashion designers, including Diane von Furstenberg, Betsey Johnson, Isaac Mizrahi, Nicole Miller, Patricia Underwood, Elie Tahari, Nanette Lepore, Juicy Couture, Rebecca Minkoff, Carlos Falchi, Doo.Ri Chung, Lela Rose, Rebecca Taylor, Prabal Gurung and others.\xa0 So cool!\xa0 Here are the details:</p>\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>The Fashion Center <em>Tour de Fashion</em></strong><br>\nThursday, September 8 \u2013 Thursday, September 15<br>\nWeekdays 10:00 am \u2013 6:00 pm; Weekends 11:00 am \u2013 6:00 pm<br>\nTented bike stations will be located on the <strong>Broadway Plazas at 40th Street</strong>.</p>\n<p style="text-align:center"><a href="http://leberpr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/tourdefashion.jpg"><img style="border:1px solid black" title="tour de fashion" src="http://leberpr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/tourdefashion.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="374"></a></p>\n<p style="text-align:center"><a href="http://leberpr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/123991936CarolynLeber97201143929PM.jpg"><img style="border:1px solid black" title="tour de fashion" src="http://leberpr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/123991936CarolynLeber97201143929PM.jpg" alt="" width="498" height="422"></a></p>\