igs/~4/YmGmFy61cnc" height="1" width="1"></p>', 
    'tag%3Agoogle.com%2C2005%3Areader/item/6b97522850fca1c4.html':'<p></p><p style="text-align:left"><a href="http://leberpr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/121224865CarolynLeber8162011100923AM.jpg"><img style="border:1px solid black" title="jane fonda and tulia" src="http://leberpr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/121224865CarolynLeber8162011100923AM.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="600"></a>I love that Jane Fonda totes little Tulia with her everywhere \u2013 I wish I could do that with my two pups who get left behind in the care of dog walkers more than I bet they like.\xa0 Yesterday Jane was doing a reading at Barnes &amp; Noble at The Grove in Los Angeles with the little fluff ball firmly tucked under her arm.\xa0 Jane is promoting her new book \u201cPrime Time\u201d and has been hopping from coast to coast quite a bit \u2013 <a href="http://janefonda.com/category/my-blog">you can read all about it on her blog</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align:center"><a href="http://leberpr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/121224878CarolynLeber8162011100942AM.jpg"><img style="border:1px solid black" title="jane fonda at barnes and noble" src="http://leberpr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/121224878CarolynLeber8162011100942AM.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="416"></a></p>\n<p align="left"><a href="http://twitter.com/home/?status=@bloomacious+Jane+Fonda+and+Tulia+are+inseperable+http://leberpr.com/blog/?p=1904" title="Post to Twitter"><img src="http://leberpr.com/blog/wp-content/plugins/tweet-this/icons/tt-twitter-big2.png" alt="Post to Twitter"></a></p><div style="height:40px"></div><div>\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/BloomaciousDigs?a=EVhEcoj9k2c:4LPjZW1Kmu8:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/BloomaciousDigs?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/BloomaciousDigs?a=EVhEcoj9k2c:4LPjZW1Kmu8:7Q72WNTAKBA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/BloomaciousDigs?d=7Q72WNTAKBA" border="0"></a> <a href="http://f