    'tag%3Agoogle.com%2C2005%3Areader/item/b2c0fc101ad15734.html':'<p><a href="http://www.benjaminhubert.co.uk">Benjamin Hubert</a> has designed the Gabion Table for <a href="http://www.delaespada.com">De La Espada</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align:center"><img title="ga_031011_01" src="http://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/ga_031011_01-630x420.jpg" alt="" width="630" height="420"></p>\n<p style="text-align:center"><span></span></p>\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color:#ffffff">.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align:left">Description from the designer:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style="text-align:left">A pedestal dining table with a metal cage base containing the ballast that creates the structures stability.</p>\n<p>Subverting the idea of traditionally hiding ballast in pedestal tables, most commonly sandbags, the dining table utilises an overt granite ballast as its focal point within a steel frame with ash surface.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<a href="http://www.contemporist.com/2011/10/03/gabion-table-by-benjamin-hubert-for-de-la-espada/ga_031011_01/" title="ga_031011_01"><img width="200" height="200" src="http://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/ga_031011_01-200x200.jpg" alt="ga_031011_01" title="ga_031011_01"></a>\n<a href="http://www.contemporist.com/2011/10/03/gabion-table-by-benjamin-hubert-for-de-la-espada/ga_031011_02/" title="ga_031011_02"><img width="200" height="200" src="http://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/ga_031011_02-200x200.jpg" alt="ga_031011_02" title="ga_031011_02"></a>\n<a href="http://www.contemporist.com/2011/10/03/gabion-table-by-benjamin-hubert-for-de-la-espada/ga_031011_03/" title="ga_031011_03"><img width="200" height="200" src="http://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/ga_031011_03-200x200.jpg" alt="ga_031011_03" title="ga_031011_03"></a>\n<a href="http://www.contemporist.com/2011/10/03/gabion-table-by-benjamin-hubert-for-de-la-espada/ga_031011_05/" title="ga_031011_05"><img width=