    'tag%3Agoogle.com%2C2005%3Areader/item/5b14bf53b813a2dd.html':'<p><a href="http://fashionista.com/2011/10/fashion-news-roundup-anna-dello-russo-wears-a-kanye-west-dress-the-queen-would-be-annoyed-if-kate-middleton-covers-vogue-and-the-lady-gaga-effect/"><img src="http://fashionista.com/uploads/2011/10/anna-dello-russo-dw-kanye-west-150x114.jpg" style="float:left;margin:0 15px 15px 0"></a><p><strong>Anna Dello Russo Wore Kanye West Three Days After His Show:</strong> Possibly his sole endorsement, but a pretty large one at that. So far, though, an ADR plug isn\u2019t quite enough to <a href="http://fashionista.com/2011/10/the-critics-arent-done-with-kanye-yet-plus-what-anna-wintour-had-to-say-about-his-debut-collection/">keep the critics at bay.</a> {<a href="http://style.mtv.com/2011/10/05/anna-dello-russo-dw-kanye-west/">MTV Style</a>}</p>\n<p><strong>The Queen Nixes a <a href="http://fashionista.com/2011/09/palace-says-kate-middleton-wont-be-appearing-on-the-cover-of-vogue-for-now/">K.Mid <em>Vogue</em> Cover</a>:</strong> A palace source said the Queen \u201cwould not be amused\u2026 Her Majesty is a real genius at making people squirm with simply a look or a \u2018tut, tut.\u2019\u201d Style icon isn\u2019t really part of Kate\u2019s Princess duties, apparently. {<a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/10/05/queen-kate-middleton-vogue-cover_n_996671.html">HuffPo</a>}</p>\n<p><strong>Katy Perry Launching a Second Fragrance:</strong> The \u201csequel\u201d to Purr comes out in November as a Nordstrom exclusive. The name remains a secret, but Perry is tweeting clues; lucky guessers will win prizes! Participate if you care. {<a href="http://www.wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/perrys-second-scent-5269813?module=today"><em>WWD</em></a>}</p>\n<p><strong><a href="http://fashionista.com/2011/10/fashion-news-roundup-anna-dello-russo-wears-a-kanye-west-dress-the-queen-would-be-annoyed-if-kate-middleton-covers-vogue-and-the-lady-gaga-effect/">Continue reading \x