    'tag%3Agoogle.com%2C2005%3Areader/item/302099a28e29c047.html':'<p><a href="http://fashionista.com/2011/10/forget-shoes-and-handbags-just-for-a-moment-your-tech-gear-needs-cute-accessories-too/"><img src="http://fashionista.com/uploads/2011/09/laptop-150x197.jpg" style="float:left;margin:0 15px 15px 0"></a><p>Technology is great and all (and we couldn\u2019t survive without it), but let\u2019s be honest: it\u2019s not always great looking. Touchscreens, portable readers and laptops have traditionally been boxy and boring. While that trend is slowly changing as tech becomes sleeker, fashion is helping to speed the process up a bit. Luckily, designers know that [...]</p>\n<p><strong><a href="http://fashionista.com/2011/10/forget-shoes-and-handbags-just-for-a-moment-your-tech-gear-needs-cute-accessories-too/">Continue reading \xbb</a></strong></p><hr style="clear:both"><h3 style="text-align:center"><em>Follow Fashionista on <a href="http://twitter.com/Fashionista_com">Twitter</a> or become a fan on <a href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Fashionistacom/93829151519">Facebook</a>.</em></h3><hr><p><iframe src="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~ah/f/ltrk2f94jsu2vikemgiavpcm94/300/250?ca=1&amp;fh=280#http%3A%2F%2Ffashionista.com%2F2011%2F10%2Fforget-shoes-and-handbags-just-for-a-moment-your-tech-gear-needs-cute-accessories-too%2F" width="100%" height="280" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0"></iframe></p><div>\n<a href="http://feeds.fashionista.com/~ff/fashionistacom?a=PPEGkupmpJo:9oAbpXDAYRY:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/fashionistacom?i=PPEGkupmpJo:9oAbpXDAYRY:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.fashionista.com/~ff/fashionistacom?a=PPEGkupmpJo:9oAbpXDAYRY:I9og5sOYxJI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/fashionistacom?d=I9og5sOYxJI" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.fashionista.com/~ff/fashionistacom?a=PPEGkupmpJo:9oAbpXDAYRY:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/fashionistaco